{"id": 2535, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今在网上发言，你都学会了哪些预防杠精的策略？", "description": "“狗头保平安”早就不够用了，为了发一句话，可能得先发十句话解释动机。哪些“友军护身符”现在已经是你在网上发言的标配了？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 2040, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180922145221LyIYOvUe8CwrmqfG.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-23T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 300032, "content": "只发表结果，不评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429298}, {"id": 300288, "content": "拉黑，举报", "image": "img/option/option/20180925151325vn19GewOTPZDB6Ad", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1443020}, {"id": 300033, "content": "我个人认为…", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714571}, {"id": 301825, "content": "杠精本精", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458860}, {"id": 302337, "content": "告诉大家，谁都别理他", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462397}, {"id": 300034, "content": "不接受反驳 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438927}, {"id": 300035, "content": "不参与 看他们杠", "image": null, "praise_count": 555, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438927}, {"id": 301060, "content": "用他的技能打败他", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454231}, {"id": 300037, "content": "预防性拉黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412106}, {"id": 300038, "content": "沉默是金", "image": null, "praise_count": 262, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665111}, {"id": 300039, "content": "先下手为强啊", "image": "img/option/option/20180924025456VFnbGd9fa1C2Qoyp.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149075}, {"id": 300040, "content": "我觉得……算了我还不评论了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 216, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240486}, {"id": 300297, "content": "一击必杀，杠精之所以杠，是他还在兴高采烈，先让他冷静下来，不论用什么方法。", "image": "img/option/option/20180925161222nK6GMdI3NaUSrEW4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039287}, {"id": 300042, "content": "🌚", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771335}, {"id": 300043, "content": "安静如鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1448726}, {"id": 300044, "content": "躲远点看着就行，不要试图教育钢筋", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018860}, {"id": 300046, "content": "多观察，不站队，少下结论", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800698}, {"id": 301070, "content": "当然是连骂带怼，你杠，老子比你更杠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455092}, {"id": 300047, "content": "对对对！你说的对！", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450440}, {"id": 300048, "content": "怼过去", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447390}, {"id": 300562, "content": "防患于未然，评论记得加狗头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610289}, {"id": 301842, "content": "不是……算了，我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573837}, {"id": 300051, "content": "夏虫不可语冰", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160463}, {"id": 300052, "content": "他们在说什么？我什么都不知道？我什么都不想听┐（─__─）┌", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1170451}, {"id": 300564, "content": "与天斗其乐无穷\n与地斗其乐无穷\n与人斗其乐无穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800975}, {"id": 300053, "content": "笑一笑就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875378}, {"id": 300054, "content": "遇到杠精直接骂，毕竟文明是为文明人准备的，对待野蛮人就应该用对待野蛮人的方式。", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155523}, {"id": 300055, "content": "当作没看到呗，想杠他什么话都能杠。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337399}, {"id": 300056, "content": "不杠，我是话题终结者", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393056}, {"id": 300057, "content": "不喜勿喷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 917725}, {"id": 300313, "content": "不回复。。。发布完观点就拍拍屁股走人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825676}, {"id": 300058, "content": "保持微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234107}, {"id": 300059, "content": "沉默，吃瓜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446050}, {"id": 300060, "content": "“讲真...”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450480}, {"id": 300572, "content": "不看抬杠，为他们智商担忧，不为自己找堵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453512}, {"id": 300061, "content": "txtx", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341628}, {"id": 300573, "content": "以开玩笑的口吻提出质疑    认真！你就输了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001167}, {"id": 300062, "content": "钢筋是自由言论的一部分🐶", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127691}, {"id": 300064, "content": "原谅无知", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1161650}, {"id": 300066, "content": "顶锅盖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449448}, {"id": 300067, "content": "？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311284}, {"id": 301603, "content": "以常识鉴别真伪，用逻辑剔除愚顽。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457503}, {"id": 300068, "content": "只能厚葬友军了😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450493}, {"id": 300324, "content": "不拒绝杠精，甚至提醒自己要记得抬杠，因为有时候被“抬杠”很能让人发现自己的盲点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378075}, {"id": 300069, "content": "能怼就怼，刚不过就关闭评论吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427396}, {"id": 300325, "content": "看sz自娱自乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451893}, {"id": 301861, "content": "没空", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458719}, {"id": 304677, "content": "行吧，我不跟他一般见识", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473677}, {"id": 300070, "content": "发好友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449144}, {"id": 300071, "content": "千万不要回复他们，也千万不要跟他们讲逻辑，讲统计学，讲道理，因为他们真的有很多时间来跟你强词夺理且智商够低认为自己比数据更正确", "image": null, "praise_count": 156, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238905}]}